<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
	<key>CAPACITOR_DEBUG</key>
	<string>$(CAPACITOR_DEBUG)</string>
	<key>CFBundleDevelopmentRegion</key>
	<string>en</string>
	<key>CFBundleDisplayName</key>
	<string>Clinike</string>
	<key>CFBundleExecutable</key>
	<string>$(EXECUTABLE_NAME)</string>
	<key>CFBundleIdentifier</key>
	<string>$(PRODUCT_BUNDLE_IDENTIFIER)</string>
	<key>CFBundleInfoDictionaryVersion</key>
	<string>6.0</string>
	<key>CFBundleName</key>
	<string>$(PRODUCT_NAME)</string>
	<key>CFBundlePackageType</key>
	<string>APPL</string>
	<key>CFBundleShortVersionString</key>
	<string>$(MARKETING_VERSION)</string>
	<key>CFBundleVersion</key>
	<string>$(CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION)</string>
	<key>LSRequiresIPhoneOS</key>
	<true/>
	<key>NSCameraUsageDescription</key>
	<string>O Clinike usa a câmera para que profissionais de saúde possam fotografar regiões tratadas — por exemplo, registrar fotos antes e depois de procedimentos estéticos como botox ou preenchimento — diretamente no prontuário do paciente.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>O Clinike usa o microfone para gravar mensagens de áudio enviadas aos pacientes pelo WhatsApp diretamente do sistema.</string>
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryAddUsageDescription</key>
	<string>O Clinike salva fotos de procedimentos estéticos — como registros antes e depois de aplicações de botox ou preenchimento — na galeria do dispositivo para backup e compartilhamento com o paciente.</string>
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
	<string>O Clinike acessa a galeria para que profissionais possam selecionar fotos existentes — por exemplo, imagens de procedimentos anteriores — e anexá-las ao prontuário do paciente.</string>
	<key>UILaunchStoryboardName</key>
	<string>LaunchScreen</string>
	<key>UIMainStoryboardFile</key>
	<string>Main</string>
	<key>UIRequiredDeviceCapabilities</key>
	<array>
		<string>armv7</string>
	</array>
	<key>UISupportedInterfaceOrientations</key>
	<array>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationPortrait</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeLeft</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeRight</string>
	</array>
	<key>UISupportedInterfaceOrientations~ipad</key>
	<array>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationPortrait</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationPortraitUpsideDown</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeLeft</string>
		<string>UIInterfaceOrientationLandscapeRight</string>
	</array>
	<key>UIViewControllerBasedStatusBarAppearance</key>
	<true/>
	<key>ITSAppUsesNonExemptEncryption</key>
	<false/>

	<key>NSFaceIDUsageDescription</key>
	<string>Use o Face ID para entrar no Clinike com segurança</string>
</dict>
</plist>
